title: Atlanta
plot: Earn and his cousin Alfred, based in Atlanta, try to make their way in the world through the rap scene. Along the way they come face-to-face with social and economic issues touching on race, relationships, poverty, status, and parenthood.
awards: Top rated TV #126 | Won 6 Primetime Emmys, 58 wins & 137 nominations total
stars: Donald Glover, Brian Tyree Henry, LaKeith Stanfield
